articles.author: Peter Aitken
articles.title: European farmers fed up with climate policies shock political establishment - Fox News
articles.description: The Farmer-Citizen Movement party, or BoerBurgerBeweging, will take 15 seats, marking the largest single-party presence in the Dutch Senate for the coming term.
articles.content:
A young Dutch political party seeking to push back on the government's climate agenda achieved a stunning victory Wednesday as it won the most seats for a single party in the Dutch Senate.
